<h1 id="inconvenience-when-we-first-met-this-ui">Inconvenience when we first met this UI</h1>
<p><img src="/sejonghudwebsite/images/incv1.png" alt="inconv" /></p>

<h3 id="red-part">Red part</h3>

<p>There are so many irregular courses in the top part of list. If we want to access our course, we should scroll down again and again.</p>

<h3 id="blue-part">Blue part</h3>

<p>In this part, the tile with regulard course is extraordinary stretched along the width of website.</p>

<h3 id="yellow-part">Yellow part</h3>

<p>Callendar is so small that we cannot observe our schedules directly.</p>

